Currency converter - An extension for Alfred based on Google Currency Converter.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------.
A default target currency can be set in the script (default = EUR), and the extension can be used in different ways, with 3-letter currency codes or the following currency symbols: $, €, £, ¥.

convert 1 GBP to EUR
convert 1.234 USD GBP
convert 1.2 $ to £
convert 2.345 SEK
convert 2.345 $
(-> the last two convert to the default currency)